snippet: Investigators were trying to determine on Monday what set off a gun battle at a weekend dance near Fresno staged by a motorcycle club that left one man dead and 13 people wounded.
abstract: Investigators are trying to determine what set off gun battle at weekend dance staged by motorcycle club near Fresno, Calif, that left one man dead and 13 people wounded.
lead_paragraph: Investigators were trying to determine on Monday what set off a gun battle at a weekend dance near Fresno staged by a motorcycle club that left one man dead and 13 people wounded.

headline.main: California: One Dead and 13 Hurt in Gunfight at Dance
